*********************************************************************
******************** INTERACTION OF DIFFRACTONS *********************
*********************************************************************

Code to generate the plot comparing different numerical methods and 
     resolutions in the section Counter-propagating collision.
** Run plot_to_paper.py to generate the plots in the paper. 
** Within the folder FV_simulations one can find the code to run 
   each of the simulations; i.e., sharpclaw on both grids and 
   clawpack on the finer grid. 

